    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-gloss finish with absolutely zero chips, dings, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats still carry that new-car scent, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership with a complete binder of meticulous maintenance records included. From the pristine alloy wheels to the untouched undercarriage, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
